1N: EEG Mirror
Your mind becomes the exhibit. The Brain Mirror translates your real-time brain activity into evolving visual forms. Powered by 204.ai generative technology and MuLabs neurofeedback, the installation responds to shifts in attention, focus, and mental engagement. As you concentrate, the imagery transforms, turning your internal cognitive state into a living artwork.
