Hulaween
Halloween got a whole lot spookier when we got involved. In Florida's famous Hulaween theres a lake named "Spirit Lake" known for being haunted. No one really knows what lives inside. This inspired us to create the Spirit Mirror where participants can be transformed into the spirits that we imagine live inside.
